data.description: WELCOME TO THIS STUNNING, LIKE NEW 4 BED | 3 BATH HOME CONVENIENTLY LOCATED TO ALL THAT SENOIA HAS TO OFFER!  This home features an inviting rocking chair front porch, an open concept floor plan & the perfect game day patio!  The kitchen offers stainless appliances, gas cooktop, an oversized kitchen island that overlooks the family room and an eat-in breakfast nook.  MASTER ON MAIN features a spacious master bath including double vanity, garden tub, separate tile shower and his & hers walk in closets!  A separate dining room, additional bedroom, full bathroom & laundry room complete the main floor.  Head upstairs to 2 very spacious bedrooms both w/ walk-in closets and a full bathroom.  Use the sliding glass door to enjoy the fully fenced back yard, extended & covered patio & newly finished rock wall feature complete with built in lighting, a fire pit and additional space to play or entertain.  Highly desirable Senoia location with walkable and golf cart friendly paths that lead to Downtown Senoia!  Call today to schedule your showing appointment!
